summary: A patch that makes the new food  from CACO work with Imps More Complex Needs
descriptionHtml:
[size=6]                    Imps More Complex Needs and CACO [/size][size=6]Patch

             [size=4]I thought that Imps More Complex Needs was an under appreciated needs mod that's why i still use it. 
[/size] [size=4]Complete Alchemy And Cooking adds a lot of new foods and I made a patch so they would work with Imps More Complex Needs. I have released the patch for anyone who wants it. [/size]
